<plot>Set in San Francisco at the end of the depression, "The Runaway", is a fable about a homeless man named Henry Blossom who is unexpectedly befriended by a nine-year old runaway girl named Lillie Whitaker. A partnership forms and a friendship blossoms, as the two become a successful street-performing duo. Meanwhile, both the police and Lillie's rich and powerful father J.W. Whitaker and socialite mother, search for their abducted daughter.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?588078</url></doc>
